Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Armageddon Can Wait
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxbsk
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 22 Nov 2002
Alistair Cooke contemplates what he considers to be; 'the striking resemblance of the events of the past year or so to the chronicles of the Bible'.